=80=9CThe old-school media and the way that we=E2=80=99ve done it=E2=80=94w=
hich is to be on a network and so forth=E2=80=94is not the way of the futur=
e.=E2=80=9D <br/><br/>Translation: LIV, which of course is financed by the =
sovereign wealth fund of Saudi Arabia, still can=E2=80=99t work out a real =
